    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1980-02-08T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1980-02-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="253"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d253">
                <head>253. Memorandum From Secretary of State <persName corresp="#p_VCR_1"
                        >Vance</persName> to President <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1"
                        >Carter</persName>
                    <note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d253fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Affairs, Brzezinski Material, <persName corresp="#p_BZK_1"
                            >Brzezinski</persName> Office File, Country Chron File, Box 44,
                        Rhodesia: 1980. Confidential.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1980-02-08">February 8, 1980</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <list type="subject">
                    <head>SUBJECT</head>
                    <item>Diplomatic Relations with Zimbabwe</item>
                </list>
                <p>Assuming that the transition to genuine majority rule is accomplished through
                    free and fair elections, we will want to establish diplomatic relations with the
                    independent state of Zimbabwe as soon as practicable, and to open an embassy
                    there. The establishment of an eight man mission, which we believe would be an
                    appropriate size in Salisbury is expected to cost approximately $1,478,000 in
                        <gloss target="#t_FY_1">FY</gloss>–80 and would require no further
                    appropriated funds.</p>
                <p>It would be helpful to have your approval in advance so that planning may
                        begin.<note n="2" xml:id="d253fn2">
                        <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1">Carter</persName> checked the approve
                        option.</note>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
